{"tid":2031776,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2少年上周破壞喜茶收銀機 被控刑毀 1人還柙兒童院 1人以10萬元保釋","createTime":"2020-05-23T15:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T13:41:16.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"270d8d40bc18ab61fb275cba2bfe7aa61714073d","tid":2031776,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"2少年破壞飲品店收銀機被控刑毀1人還柙兒童院<br />\n23.05.2020 23:06<br />\n<br />\n兩名15歲少年上周三闖入沙田新城市廣場一間「喜茶」飲品店，破壞收銀機等設施，被埋伏的便衣警員拘捕，被控刑事毀壞，在粉嶺裁判法院少年法庭提堂，其中一人要還柙兒童院，另一人獲准以10萬元保釋，需要遵守宵禁令和禁足有關商場，案件下月29日再提堂。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，兩人在店內損壞兩部收銀機顯示屏和一部八達通處理器，總值約15,000元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289687&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289687%26csid%3D261_341&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOQEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=9c92c666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289687&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"96bb806bec8494095dda7f21b1fe94c3e1e4bff2","tid":2031776,"uid":105340,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"妖 咁多便衣<br />\n點解班細路唔忍下"}]}